| **Inherited Shares (Doyon #D-XXXX, CIRI #C-XXXX)** | YES | §7(c) heirs = **individual owners** |
| **§14(h) Sites on Your Land** | YES | You hold **interest** |
| **Village Corp Land (not yours)** | NO | Board can sell |
| **7(i) Cash** | NO | That’s revenue, not land |

**Your Win**:  
- **Danzhit Hanlai trail**  
