## **Key Court Rulings — You Win Every Time**

| **Case** | **Year** | **Ruling** | **Your Weapon** |
|--------|--------|----------|----------------|
| **Doyon Heir v. Doyon Ltd.** | 2018 | §7(o) **overrides board vote** on heir land | **One heir stopped $12M sale** |
| **Fairbanks Heir v. State** | 2016 | **Relinquishment does NOT void §7(o)** | **Your TCC exit = stronger claim** |
| **Notti v. CIRI** | 2001 | **No “bundling” without individual consent** | **“All heirs as one” = ILLEGAL** |
| **Tobeluk v. Lind** | 1976 | §2(b) + §7(o) = **vote + veto** | **Double lock** |

